                Ge<lb break="no" n="2"/>ni<lb break="no" n="3"/>o <lb n="4"/>|(centuriae) </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> Ge<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>io |(centuriae) </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>AT</abbr><ex cert="low"/>inia</expan> <expan><abbr>AT</abbr><ex cert="low"/>T</expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>E<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>de suo posu<supplied reason="lost">it <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex cert="low"/>I</expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> An<supplied reason="lost">tonino <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Statuette eines an einem Altar opfernden Genius. Die Inschriften befinden sich auf dem Altar (Z. 1-4) und der niederen, in einem Stück mit der Statuette gearbeiteten Basis (Z. 5-8); Z. 5 steht auf dem leicht vorspringenden oberen Absatz der Basis. Oberfläche teilweise stark verrieben. (B): Jacobi; CIL 13, 07450; Mattern: kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
